From 4924b228cc1ce69725c8339f464cbe6fa924331f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <fix@alaruel>
Date: Tue, 17 Mar 2026 18:30:45 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix map image display + add encounter planner to sessions
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Fix assets:resolve to return base64 data URL instead of file:// URL.
  Electron sandbox (sandbox:true) blocks file:// in renderer; base64
  data URLs load fine without relaxing security.
- Rewrite SessionsView with three-tab layout: Encounters / Prep / Notes
- Encounters tab is a modular encounter planner backed by session_scenes:
  - Add/edit/delete encounters with title, type, objective, setup, reward
  - Types: Combat, Roleplay, Exploration, Puzzle, Social, Rest, Revelation,
    Travel, Other (each with emoji icon pill)
  - Reorder encounters up/down
  - Expand card to see full detail or inline edit form
  - Toggle played/unplayed per encounter (numbered circle → checkmark)
  - Summary line shows X/N completed
- Prep and Notes tabs unchanged in functionality, just reorganised under tabs
